        <abstract> 
<p>Sends a paper on reproductive modes of <hi rend="italic">Leptodera</hi> ["Organisation und Fortpflanzen von <hi rend="italic">Leptodera</hi>", <hi rend="italic">Schr. Ges. Beförd. Naturw. Marburg</hi> (1869)].</p> 
            <p>Criticises Ernst Haeckel’s work as too unripe and enthusiastic.</p>
            <p>Asks CD for some specimens of cirripedes in pupal stage for a work in progress.</p>
        </abstract>
